OL,6,FJailing her for a total of 20 months
OL,7,Ffor her latest offences, Judge Julie
OL,8,FWarburton said: "You have a prolific
OL,9,Frecord for offending in the same way
OL,10,For a similar nature with 135
OL,11,Fappearances for 332 offences of which
OL,12,Fa significant number are for thefts.
OL,14,F"I accept your main mitigation is your
OL,15,Fguilty plea and you have plainly been
OL,16,Ftrapped in a lifestyle which has left
OL,17,Fyou entrenched in a pattern of
OL,18,Foffending over many years.
